{# packs/events-management/templates/speaker-outreach-email.md.j2
   Jinja2 template for personalised speaker outreach emails.
   Rendered by speaker-outreach-drafter agent.
   Requires human approval before send.

   Context variables:
     speaker.name           — speaker full name
     speaker.email          — speaker email
     speaker.bio            — speaker bio (used for personalisation)
     speaker.company        — speaker's company
     session.title          — session title
     session.theme          — session track / theme
     session.format         — talk | workshop | panel | keynote | lightning
     session.duration_min   — duration in minutes
     event.name             — event name
     event.starts_at        — event start datetime
     event.ends_at          — event end datetime
     event.venue            — venue name (may be null for virtual)
     email_type             — 'invitation' | 'confirmation'
     speaker.calendly_link  — Calendly scheduling link (invitation only)
     resource_portal_url    — speaker resource portal URL (confirmation only)
     slide_deadline         — slide submission deadline date (confirmation only)
     llm_body               — LLM-drafted personalised body paragraph(s)
     sender_name            — event team sender name
     sender_title           — event team sender title
#}

Subject: {% if email_type == 'invitation' %}
Speaking Invitation — {{ session.title }} at {{ event.name }}
{% else %}
Your Session is Confirmed — {{ event.name }} Speaker Resources
{% endif %}

---

Hi {{ speaker.name | first_name }},

{{ llm_body }}

---

**Session Details**

| Field    | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Session  | {{ session.title }} |
| Track    | {{ session.theme | default('TBD') }} |
| Format   | {{ session.format | title }} ({{ session.duration_min }} min) |
| Event    | {{ event.name }} |
| Date     | {{ event.starts_at | date_format('%B %-d, %Y') }}{% if event.ends_at and event.ends_at != event.starts_at %} – {{ event.ends_at | date_format('%B %-d, %Y') }}{% endif %} |
| Venue    | {{ event.venue | default('Virtual') }} |

{% if email_type == 'invitation' %}
**Next step:** Please confirm your availability using the link below so we can
lock in your session slot:

[Confirm your session →]({{ speaker.calendly_link }})

If you have any questions before confirming, reply to this email and we will
get back to you within one business day.
{% else %}
**Speaker Resources**

Everything you need is in the Speaker Resource Portal:

[Access your speaker portal →]({{ resource_portal_url }})

**Slide submission deadline:** {{ slide_deadline | date_format('%B %-d, %Y') }}

Please upload your slides as PDF or PowerPoint. Our content team will review
and provide feedback within 3 business days.
{% endif %}

---

Looking forward to having you at {{ event.name }}!

Warm regards,
{{ sender_name }}
{{ sender_title }}

{# Deferred: add calendar .ics attachment when calendar-export tool is wired #}
